The paper deals with a wireless communication system, which suggests that it could belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT) or Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. The use of multiantenna base station and single-antenna users indicates that it could also belong to the Signal Processing (cs.SY) or Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Finally, the proposed algorithm involves solving convex problems, which suggests that it could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category.
